Yes, there was a recall on bus heat exchangers , back in the late 90's I think. I bought a '72 from a friend of mine, and he got the heat exchangers on that bus replaced under the recall. He said an old German mechanic that VW rehired out of retiremant came to his house and did the work in his driveway.   Jeff
